<p rend="centre"><hi rend="underline">Signatures of the Trustees elected at the said Meeting.</hi></p> 
<p rend="centre"><hi rend="underline">Each Trustee must sign his Christian and Surname, and state his Occupation and Place of Residence at full length underneath.</hi></p> 
<table><row><cell cols="2">Charles Pearson Schoolmaster</cell></row>
<row><cell/><cell>Down Kent</cell></row>
<row><cell cols="2">Charles Robert Darwin,</cell></row>
<row><cell/><cell>no occupation, of Down, Kent</cell></row>
<row><cell cols="2">J. Brodie Innes</cell></row>
<row><cell/><cell>Clerk in Holy Orders. Milton Brodie, Forres—</cell></row></table>
<p>The Rev<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>. Robert Ainslie has left this parish many years and has not acted as a Trustee for years &amp; we know not where he is<ref target="#foot.f4"/></p>
<p>Tho<hi rend="superscript">s</hi>. Lewis Sec</p>
